<manpage>
    <sample url="sdk\operating_system\user_com_interface\elasock\sam02">gethostbyaddr</sample>
    <volume>elasock API</volume>
    <title>gethostbyaddr</title>
    <routine_idx>ElastosSocketIndex.htm</routine_idx>

    <description>
        <para>返回对应于IP地址的主机信息。</para>
    </description>

    <syntax>
        <return_val>struct hostent *</return_val>
        <parameters>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>const char *</param_type>
                <param_name>addr</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]指向网络字节顺序地址的指针。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>len</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]IP地址的长度，在AF_INET类型地址中为4。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
            <api_param>
                <param_type>int</param_type>
                <param_name>type</param_name>
                <param_note>
                    <para>[in]地址类型，例如AF_INET。</para>
                </param_note>
            </api_param>
        </parameters>
    </syntax>

    <return>
        <para>如果程序运行成功，返回一个指向<link url="DataType\hostent.htm">hostent</link>结构的指针；否则，返回一个空指针，可以通过<link url="WSAGetLastError.htm">WSAGetLastError()</link>来获得具体的错误代码。</para>
    </return>

    <remarks>
        <para>gethostbyaddr()函数返回一个指向hostent结构的指针，hostent结构中包含了主机对应的名字和地址。</para>
        <para>《Elastos》暂不支持主机多址。</para>
    </remarks>

    <requirements>
        <system>
            <system_name>
                Elastos 操作系统
            </system_name>
        </system>
        <headerfile>
            <file_name> winsock.h</file_name>
        </headerfile>
        <library>
            <lib_name> ElSocket.lib  </lib_name>
        </library>
    </requirements>

